@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

###
### 0) Health check (optional)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v3/api-docs

###
### 1) Create portfolio (copy the id from the response and paste into @portfolioId)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/portfolios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My First Portfolio"
}

###
### 2) Set this manually after step 1
@portfolioId = 0dd64ba3-605d-4bf6-93d7-0afb910b0f55

###
### 3) Get portfolio by id (before holding)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/portfolios/{{portfolioId}}

###
### 4) Add holding
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/portfolios/{{portfolioId}}/holdings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "AAPL",
  "quantity": 10
}

###
### 5) Get portfolio by id (after holding)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/portfolios/{{portfolioId}}
